SHOWLINETAB unit number_of_point offset_in_X offset_in_Y

uses the content of the TAB[] buffer as X coordinates and the
working 1D buffer as Y coordinates and draw the corresponding set of vectors.

the parameters are :
unit : the unit in which the content of TAB[] will be interpreted
number_of_point : the number of point to draw
offset_in_X , offset_in_Y the location of the drawing

Will work only in the 1D window

see also : SHOWLINE integrate

